{"content":"I uploaded a CSV called \"tickets.csv\" (blob id 5be48fea-9c69-4769-a639-13549d019598). It has columns ticket_id, subject, body, customer_tier, amount. Build a pipeline that splits rows into two JSONL files based on customer_tier: rows where customer_tier == 'enterprise' go to high_priority.jsonl, everything else goes to low_priority.jsonl. Quarantine any source-validation failures."}
